WEBVTT

00:02.291 --> 00:05.735
Kate's assistant, Liam... Could be
the son she gave up for adoption.

00:05.745 --> 00:08.145
Your company's secure
data has been breached.

00:08.214 --> 00:09.670
Kate was onto Liam.

00:09.680 --> 00:11.580
We're not gonna tell
the police anything.

00:11.682 --> 00:14.950
Did it ever occur to you that Liam
may have killed Kate to cover it up?

00:15.052 --> 00:17.586
I'm looking for her. Her name is Carly.

00:17.688 --> 00:19.088
How did you get that photo?

00:19.190 --> 00:21.190
Your wife sent it to me
right before she died.

00:21.325 --> 00:22.658
Where's Liam?

00:22.760 --> 00:24.460
Yeah, she knows where Liam is,

00:24.562 --> 00:26.896
but she's not talking... Yet.

00:31.669 --> 00:33.402
Yeah, I see you doing the math.

00:33.504 --> 00:36.572
Do you run? Dial 911?

00:36.674 --> 00:38.440
Problem is, you want answers.

00:38.543 --> 00:41.777
And by the time the cops show,
me and her will be gone.

00:41.913 --> 00:46.048
So are you staying, or are you going?

00:46.646 --> 00:48.329
You won't hurt her?

00:49.571 --> 00:51.289
That's up to her.

00:55.310 --> 00:57.393
I need answers.

00:57.495 --> 01:01.330
Look, Liam is a con man, a criminal.

01:01.432 --> 01:04.233
Stepping into this world,
you need to know two things...

01:04.334 --> 01:06.669
Everyone's lying,

01:06.771 --> 01:09.438
and stay out of my way.

01:09.540 --> 01:11.507
So, where's your boyfriend at?

01:11.609 --> 01:13.842
I told you he's not my boyfriend.

01:13.945 --> 01:15.911
I met him out maybe a month ago.

01:16.013 --> 01:19.448
Okay, and he bought
you a 79-inch 3-D TV?

01:19.458 --> 01:21.917
I just thought he really liked me.

01:22.019 --> 01:24.386
So Liam, the legit assistant,

01:24.488 --> 01:26.488
blew 30 grand on a month-long crush?

01:26.981 --> 01:29.291
Really?! That's your story?!

01:29.589 --> 01:31.060
Are you that dumb?!

01:33.297 --> 01:34.931
Look, give it up.

01:36.856 --> 01:39.323
I'm not buying the
babe in the woods act.

01:39.446 --> 01:42.908
You are gonna call Liam
and get him to meet you.

01:45.109 --> 01:47.409
- I told you...
- No. Look.

01:48.813 --> 01:51.680
You are gonna call Liam

01:51.782 --> 01:54.149
and get him to meet you.

01:54.676 --> 01:56.051
Now.

02:00.728 --> 02:01.944
Where?

02:03.094 --> 02:05.261
Dinah's in south Tryon.

02:09.076 --> 02:10.705
What's your name?

02:12.494 --> 02:13.842
Doesn't matter.

02:15.239 --> 02:17.172
What happens if she warns him?

02:17.275 --> 02:19.074
What happens if you warn him?

02:19.897 --> 02:22.344
Something bad.

